    <item>
      <title>Robinhood 为“成熟”交易者推出新工具</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-17/robinhood-launches-new-tools-for-sophisticated-traders-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Robinhood 创始人兼首席执行官 Vlad Tenev 谈到了其用来吸引更多“成熟投资者”加入平台的新工具。客户将能够交易更多期货合约。Tenev 还表示，客户正在寻找有关美国总统大选的更准确信息。他正在“彭博未平仓合约”上。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-17/robinhood-launches-new-tools-for-sophisticated-traders-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 14:53:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非 1690 亿美元基金经理正在寻找新 CEO</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/south-africa-s-169-billion-fund-manager-is-seeking-new-ceo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[管理着 3 万亿兰特（1690 亿美元）资产的南非公共投资公司表示，该公司正在寻找一位首席执行官，现任首席执行官将于明年退休。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/south-africa-s-169-billion-fund-manager-is-seeking-new-ceo</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 14:50:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据称法国巴黎银行将解雇新兴市场信贷团队的四名成员</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/bnp-said-to-lay-off-four-members-of-emerging-markets-credit-team</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，法国巴黎银行在扩大新兴市场信贷业务仅仅两年后，就从其新兴市场信贷团队中解雇了至少四名员工。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/bnp-said-to-lay-off-four-members-of-emerging-markets-credit-team</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 14:44:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卢森堡贝特尔：移民政策需要团结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-17/luxembourg-s-bettel-need-solidarity-in-migration-policy-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[卢森堡外交部长兼副首相泽维尔·贝特尔在与彭博社记者奥利弗·克鲁克的对话中讨论了欧洲关于移民政策的争论，因为这已成为欧盟领导人之间的关键分界线。他们还讨论了乌克兰总统泽连斯基面临的挑战以及欧洲对中国的态度。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-17/luxembourg-s-bettel-need-solidarity-in-migration-policy-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 14:37:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
